		<string>Zealova needs access to your health data to sync measurements like weight, body fat, heart rate, VO2 max, and outdoor workout routes (GPS) from Apple Health.</string>
		<key>NSHealthUpdateUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova saves the workouts, body measurements, meals, and hydration you log to Apple Health.</string>
		<key>LSApplicationQueriesSchemes</key>
		<array>
			<string>instagram-stories</string>
			<string>instagram</string>
		</array>
		<key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova needs access to your photo library so you can pick food photos for AI nutrition analysis and progress photos for body tracking.</string>
		<key>NSPhotoLibraryAddUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova needs access to save workout recap images to your photo library.</string>
		<key>NSUserTrackingUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Allowing tracking lets Zealova personalize your AI coach recommendations and measure which features actually help users hit their goals. Data stays inside Zealova — we never sell it and we don't share it with advertisers.</string>
		<key>NSFaceIDUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova uses Face ID to keep your account and health data secure when you re-open the app.</string>
		<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova needs access to the microphone for voice-to-text food logging.</string>
		<key>NSSpeechRecognitionUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova uses speech recognition to transcribe your voice into text for food logging and exercise-swap requests.</string>
		<key>NSCameraUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova needs camera access to take food photos for AI nutrition analysis and barcode scanning.</string>
		<key>NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova needs your location to find nearby gyms and set up automatic gym profile switching.</string>
		<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova uses background location to automatically switch to your gym profile when you arrive at a saved gym location.</string>
		<key>NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription</key>
		<string>Zealova uses background location to automatically switch to your gym profile when you arrive at a saved gym location.</string>
		<!-- BLE heart-rate feature disabled. NSBluetoothAlwaysUsageDescription
		     is omitted so iOS never shows the Bluetooth prompt. If the feature
		     is re-enabled, restore the key below and the bluetooth-central
